{"type":"message","id":"3c184869","parentId":"8aba8e1c","timestamp":"2026-04-22T09:40:31.211Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"卡住了，原因很直接：\n\n**现在没配 `OPENAI_API_KEY`，所以图片接口调用不了。**\n\n你刚给的是模型/尺寸信息，不是 API key。  \n要继续生成，有两种最快路径：\n\n1. **你提供可用的 OpenAI Images API key**  \n   我就继续用 `gpt-image-1` 给你出这张图。\n\n2. **改用你本机已配置好的其他图像提供商**  \n   比如 `google / openrouter / dashscope / minimax / replicate`，前提是环境里已经有对应 key。\n\n如果你想继续走 OpenAI，直接回我：\n\n`OPENAI_API_KEY=你的key`\n\n如果你不想贴 key，我也可以立刻帮你改成一版**可直接拿去任意文生图平台使用的高质量中文提示词**。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8978aa4388193ba0908fd32def67b\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":30180,"output":191,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30371,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776850817661,"responseId":"resp_08875cf3083ad23c0169e89782eee88193bddd904788b49abc"}}
