{"type":"message","id":"a6cd581f","parentId":"348399f9","timestamp":"2026-04-22T09:44:45.346Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_p8feafDkvhSzpG3vmHJElIZF|fc_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8988bf7708193ba9ebec41fa5048f","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Using openai / gpt-image-2 for single\nSwitch model: --model <id> | EXTEND.md default_model.openai | env OPENAI_IMAGE_MODEL\n[single] Attempt 1/3 failed, retrying...\n[single] Attempt 2/3 failed, retrying...\nOpenAI API error: {\n  \"error\": {\n    \"message\": \"Incorrect API key provided: sk-bbad0*******************************************************8ea4. You can find your API key at https://platform.openai.com/account/api-keys.\",\n    \"type\": \"invalid_request_error\",\n    \"code\": \"invalid_api_key\",\n    \"param\": null\n  },\n  \"status\": 401\n}\n\n\nProcess exited with code 1."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"cool-summit","exitCode":1,"aggregated":"Using openai / gpt-image-2 for single\nSwitch model: --model <id> | EXTEND.md default_model.openai | env OPENAI_IMAGE_MODEL\n[single] Attempt 1/3 failed, retrying...\n[single] Attempt 2/3 failed, retrying...\nOpenAI API error: {\n  \"error\": {\n    \"message\": \"Incorrect API key provided: sk-bbad0*******************************************************8ea4. You can find your API key at https://platform.openai.com/account/api-keys.\",\n    \"type\": \"invalid_request_error\",\n    \"code\": \"invalid_api_key\",\n    \"param\": null\n  },\n  \"status\": 401\n}\n","name":"OPENAI_API_KEY='[REDACTED]' npx"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776851085296}}
{"type":"message","id":"af6773c9","parentId":"a6cd581f","timestamp":"2026-04-22T09:44:57.197Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这次我试了，还是失败了。\n\n**结果：你给的 key 无效，OpenAI 返回 401 `invalid_api_key`。**\n\n报错核心是：\n- `Incorrect API key provided`\n- 模型调用已经走到 OpenAI 了\n- 真正拦住的是 **key 本身不对或不可用**\n\n你可以这样处理：\n\n1. 去 OpenAI Platform 重新创建一个可用 key  \n   地址：`https://platform.openai.com/account/api-keys`\n\n2. 确认这个 key 对应的账号/项目有图片接口权限\n\n3. 重新发我，格式还是：\n   `OPENAI_API_KEY=[REDACTED]`\n\n如果你愿意，我拿到新 key 后就直接继续生成这张：\n- **哔哩哔哩直播间**\n- **蓝白女仆风格 coser**\n- **跳舞动态感**\n- **1024x1024**\n- **gpt-image-2**\n\n另外提醒一句，既然这个 key 已经发出来了，**建议你立刻作废它并重新生成一个**，更安全。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_08875cf3083ad23c0169e89892b2188193a6a0f813bd801e68\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":31565,"output":247,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31812,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776851085349,"responseId":"resp_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8988eadcc819399dbe74930b76001"}}
