{"type":"message","id":"231b9cd7","parentId":"2bc2365b","timestamp":"2026-04-22T09:45:01.051Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System (untrusted): [2026-04-22 17:44:28 GMT+8] Exec completed (cool-sum, code 1) :: pt 1/3 failed, retrying... [single] Attempt 2/3 failed, retrying... OpenAI API error: { \"error\": { \"message\": \"Incorrect API key provided: sk-bbad0********************************…\n\nAn async command you ran earlier has completed. The result is shown in the system messages above. Please relay the command output to the user in a helpful way. If the command succeeded, share the relevant output. If it failed, explain what went wrong.\nCurrent time: Wednesday, April 22nd, 2026 - 5:44 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-22 09:44 UTC"}],"timestamp":1776851100946}}
{"type":"message","id":"6c0a23b0","parentId":"231b9cd7","timestamp":"2026-04-22T09:45:13.747Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"刚刚那次异步生成也确认失败了。\n\n**失败原因**\n- 请求已经发到 OpenAI\n- 但返回的是 **401 / `invalid_api_key`**\n- 也就是：**提供的 API key 不正确或已失效**\n\n从日志看，程序还自动重试了两次，但结果一样，所以不是网络抖动。\n\n**现在最稳的做法**\n1. 先把刚才发出来的 key 作废\n2. 去 OpenAI Platform 重新生成新 key\n3. 把新 key 发我，我继续用 `gpt-image-2` 直接生成\n\n如果你暂时不想折腾 key，我也可以马上给你一版可直接复制到生图平台的提示词。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_08875cf3083ad23c0169e898a520788193881631fd39a090ea\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":31925,"output":165,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32090,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776851101051,"responseId":"resp_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8989e6f84819389c165300f0be2b3"}}
