{"type":"message","id":"cb19a7b0","parentId":"d1a8f83d","timestamp":"2026-04-22T15:10:20.898Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"可以，我理解你是想用 **OpenAI 的图片模型，输出 1024x1024**。\n\n不过现在还差两个关键信息我才能直接开画：\n\n1. **提示词 / 你想画什么**\n2. **可用的 OpenAI API key**  \n   你之前发过那个 key 已经报过 `invalid_api_key`，不能继续用。\n\n你直接按这个格式发我就行：\n\n- **主题**：比如“哔哩哔哩直播间里，蓝白女仆风 coser 跳舞”\n- **API key**：`OPENAI_API_KEY=...`\n\n如果你不想自己写提示词，也可以直接回我一句：\n\n**帮我写提示词并生成**\n\n我会先帮你补全成适合 `gpt-image` 的版本。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8e4d8ab908193a5a8dfd07b0343cf\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":34489,"output":185,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34674,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776870613583,"responseId":"resp_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8e4d75680819381a118cbc5c73121"}}
