{"type":"message","id":"a495fe47","parentId":"14f50286","timestamp":"2026-04-22T15:10:31.475Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"能。  \n你给我这两样，我就直接帮你生成：\n\n1. **画什么**，一句话就行  \n2. **可用的 OpenAI API key**，格式：\n   `OPENAI_API_KEY=...`\n\n如果你还没想好描述，直接发我这种也行：\n\n- “赛博朋克少女，雨夜街头，电影感，1024x1024”\n- “哔哩哔哩直播间里 coser 跳舞，二次元风，1024x1024”\n\n如果你不方便发 key，我也可以先免费帮你写好一版高质量提示词。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8e4e4a32081939eb54b4cf593a02e\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":34746,"output":143,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34889,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776870625183,"responseId":"resp_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8e4e27408819393cd2ea96aa50769"}}
