{"type":"message","id":"7b809016","parentId":"ef151fd0","timestamp":"2026-04-22T15:12:08.259Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我试了，两张都没跑出来。\n\n原因一样，都是：\n\n**你这串 `OPENAI_API_KEY` 不是有效的 OpenAI key。**\n\n日志返回的是：\n- `invalid_api_key`\n- `Incorrect API key provided`\n\n而且这次两张图都验证过了，不是偶发失败。\n\n### 结论\n你现在这个：\n`48ch-wzC2qzxmQIBPq8mMXbQXRi454v8`\n\n**不是 OpenAI 官方可用的 API key 格式**，所以我没法直接帮你生图。\n\n### 正常的 OpenAI key 一般是\n- `sk-...`\n- 并且来自 `platform.openai.com`\n\n### 你现在可以这样做\n1. 去这里创建新的 key  \n   `https://platform.openai.com/account/api-keys`\n\n2. 把新 key 发我  \n   格式：\n   `OPENAI_API_KEY=[REDACTED]`\n\n3. 我就继续帮你生成这两张：\n- 赛博朋克少女，雨夜街头，电影感，1024x1024\n- 哔哩哔哩直播间里 coser 跳舞，二次元风，1024x1024\n\n如果你愿意，我也可以先把这两张的**高质量提示词**整理好，你拿去任意生图平台直接用。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8e54245f08193a616f998f14f1aa2\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":36132,"output":305,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36437,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776870716888,"responseId":"resp_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8e53e2dac8193af94e703ae4cd10b"}}
