{"type":"message","id":"60c6d7de","parentId":"3c732b44","timestamp":"2026-04-22T15:17:45.497Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_o4fkpvWwcB5ccIJXgMGJ6y2d|fc_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8e6982b7481938b6847b8dc552b77","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"poll","sessionId":"good-sage","data":"","keys":[],"hex":[],"literal":"","text":"","bracketed":false,"eof":false,"offset":0,"limit":260,"timeout":30000},"partialJson":"{\"action\":\"poll\",\"sessionId\":\"good-sage\",\"data\":\"\",\"keys\":[],\"hex\":[],\"literal\":\"\",\"text\":\"\",\"bracketed\":false,\"eof\":false,\"offset\":0,\"limit\":260,\"timeout\":30000}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":37166,"output":60,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37226,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776871059926,"responseId":"resp_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8e69576888193a7630037ae3e6ac8"}}
{"type":"message","id":"60e0a4f7","parentId":"60c6d7de","timestamp":"2026-04-22T15:17:45.587Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_o4fkpvWwcB5ccIJXgMGJ6y2d|fc_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8e6982b7481938b6847b8dc552b77","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":" --show-error --no-buffer `\n    -X POST $apiUrl `\n    -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" `\n    -H \"Authorization: Bearer $apiKey\" `\n    --data-binary (\"@\" + $tempBodyFile) |\n  ForEach-Object -Begin {\n    $eventType = $null\n    $dataLines = [System.Collections.Generic.List[string]]::new()\n\n    function Save-Bytes {\n      param([string]$Path, [string]$Base64)\n      [System.IO.File]::WriteAllBytes($Path, [Convert]::FromBase64String($Base64))\n      Write-Host \"Saved $Path\"\n    }\n\n    function Save-ImageGenerationCallResult {\n      param([object]$ImageCall)\n\n      if (-not $ImageCall) { return }\n      if ($ImageCall.type -ne \"image_generation_call\") { return }\n      if (-not $ImageCall.result) { return }\n\n      $ext = if ($ImageCall.output_format) { [string]$ImageCall.output_format } else { \"png\" }\n      $path = Join-Path (Get-Location) \"$outBase.$ext\"\n      Save-Bytes -Path $path -Base64 ([string]$ImageCall.result)\n    }\n\n    function ConvertFrom-JsonCompat {\n      param([string]$Json)\n\n      if ($PSVersionTable.PSVersion.Major -ge 6) {\n        return $Json | ConvertFrom-Json -Depth 100\n      }\n\n      return $Json | ConvertFrom-Json\n    }\n\n    function Flush-SseEvent {\n      param([string]$Type, [System.Collections.Generic.List[string]]$DataLines)\n\n      if (-not $Type -or $DataLines.Count -eq 0) { return }\n\n      $json = ($DataLines -join \"`n\").Trim()\n      if (-not $json -or $json -eq \"[DONE]\") { return }\n\n      try {\n        $obj = ConvertFrom-JsonCompat -Json $json\n      } catch {\n        return\n      }\n\n      switch ($Type) {\n        \"response.output_item.done\" {\n          Save-ImageGenerationCallResult -ImageCall $obj.item\n        }\n\n        \"response.completed\" {\n          $imageCall = @(\n            $obj.response.output |\n            Where-Object { $_.type -eq \"image_generation_call\" -and $_.result }\n          ) | Select-Object -First 1\n\n          Save-ImageGenerationCallResult -ImageCall $imageCall\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  } -Process {\n    $line = [string]$_\n\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"good-sage","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"Title: 抛砖引玉，教你如何使用CLIProxyAPI来自定义GPT画图模型\n\nURL Source: https://www.nodeseek.com/post-692204-1\n\nMarkdown Content:\n# 抛砖引玉，教你如何使用CLIProxyAPI来自定义GPT画图模型\n\n**[![Image 1: logo](https://www.nodeseek.com/static/image/favicon/android-chrome-192x192.png)NodeSeek beta](https://www.nodeseek.com/)**\n*   [日常](https://www.nodeseek.com/categories/daily)\n*   [技术](https://www.nodeseek.com/categories/tech)\n*   [情报](https://www.nodeseek.com/categories/info)\n*   [测评](https://www.nodeseek.com/categories/review)\n*   [交易](https://www.nodeseek.com/categories/trade)\n*   [拼车](https://www.nodeseek.com/categories/carpool)\n*   [推广](https://www.nodeseek.com/categories/promotion)\n*   [DeepFlood](https://www.deepflood.com/)\n\n[search for post](javascript:void(0))[search for people](javascript:void(0))[use google search](javascript:void(0))\n\n#### 所有版块\n\n*   [日常](https://www.nodeseek.com/categories/daily)\n*   [技术](https://www.nodeseek.com/categories/tech)\n*   [情报](https://www.nodeseek.com/categories/info)\n*   [测评](https://www.nodeseek.com/categories/review)\n*   [交易](https://www.nodeseek.com/categories/trade)\n*   [拼车](https://www.nodeseek.com/categories/carpool)\n*   [推广](https://www.nodeseek.com/categories/promotion)\n*   [生活](https://www.nodeseek.com/categories/life)\n*   [Dev](https://www.nodeseek.com/categories/dev)\n*   [贴图](https://www.nodeseek.com/categories/photo-share)\n*   [曝光](https://www.nodeseek.com/categories/expose)\n*   [沙盒](https://www.nodeseek.com/categories/sandbox)\n\n# [抛砖引玉，教你如何使用CLIProxyAPI来自定义GPT画图模型](https://www.nodeseek.com/post-692204-1)\n\n[![Image 2: hkfires](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/23484.png)](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/23484 \"hkfires\")\n\n[hkfires](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/23484)楼主 管理\n\n4days ago in [技术](https://www.nodeseek.com/categories/tech)\n\n[#0](https://www.nodeseek.com/post-692204-1#0)\n\n昨天，在群里小伙伴的提醒下，我了解到通过反代 Codex 也可以进行图片的生成和编辑了。随即我进行了一番实验，使用 `GPT-Image-1.5` 成功生成了如下图片：\n\n![Image 3](https://img.072899.xyz/2026/04/3cb8c69fac588f10966c91f8e7b50a7b.png)\n\n#### 技术原理：工具调用（Tool Calling）\n\n与 Gemini 使用专用图片模型（如 NanoBanana 系列）的逻辑不同，在 Codex 中，生图功能是通过 **调用工具** 实现的，并不依赖特定的模型名称。\n\n基于这一特性，我们可以利用 `CLIProxyAPI` 的 **模型别名** 配合 **Payload 重写** 功能，自定义一套专属的“文生图模型”。下面我分享一下自己的配置思路和使用方法，希望能起到抛砖引玉的作用。\n\nPS：下文前提是已经安装配置好 `CLIProxyAPI` 并添加了 Codex 的 OAuth 凭证。\n\n* * *\n\n#### 1. 配置文件修改\n\n在 `CLIProxyAPI` 的配置文件中添加以下内容。这里我们将 `gpt-5.4-mini` 映射为不同分辨率的生图模型，并通过 Payload 强制开启 `image_generation` 工具。\n\n```yaml\noauth-model-alias:\n  codex:\n    - name: gpt-5.4-mini\n      alias: gpt-image-1024x1024\n      fork: true\n    - name: gpt-5.4-mini\n      alias: gpt-image-1024x1536\n      fork: true\n    - name: gpt-5.4-mini\n      alias: gpt-image-1536x1024\n      fork: true\n\npayload:\n  override-raw:\n    - models:\n        - name: gpt-image-1024x1024\n          protocol: codex\n      params:\n        tools: '[{\"type\":\"image_generation\", \"size\": \"1024x1024\", \"quality\": \"high\", \"background\": \"auto\"}]'\n        tool_choice: '{\"type\": \"image_generation\"}'\n    - models:\n        - name: gpt-image-1024x1536\n          protocol: codex\n      params:\n        tools: '[{\"type\":\"image_generation\", \"size\": \"1024x1536\", \"quality\": \"high\", \"background\": \"auto\"}]'\n        tool_choice: '{\"type\": \"image_generation\"}'\n    - models:\n        - name: gpt-image-1536x1024\n          protocol: codex\n      params:\n        tools: '[{\"type\":\"image_generation\", \"size\": \"1536x1024\", \"quality\": \"high\", \"background\": \"auto\"}]'\n        tool_choice: '{\"type\": \"image_generation\"}'\n```\n\n添加完成后，我们就可以直接调用 `gpt-image-1024x1024`、`gpt-image-1024x1536` 和 `gpt-image-1536x1024` 这三个自定义模型了。\n\n* * *\n\n#### 2. 快速调用脚本 (PowerShell)\n\n由于目前我还未找到好用的生图客户端，我编写了一个简单的 Windows PowerShell 脚本供大家参考。\n\n**使用方法：**\n\n1.   修改脚本前四行的 `apiUrl`、`apiKey` 等参数。\n2.   将完整脚本粘贴至 PowerShell 窗口运行。\n3.   等待约数十秒，即可在当前运行路径下看到生成的图片。\n\n```powershell\n$apiUrl = \"https://你的CLIProxyAPI地址/v1/responses\"\n$apiKey = \"你的CLIProxyAPI的apikey\"\n$model = \"gpt-image-1536x1024\"\n$text = \"画一张赛博朋克的香港，要有汉字\"\n\n$bodyObject = @{\n  model = $model\n  instructions = \"You are a helpful assistant.\"\n  input = @(\n    @{\n      type = \"message\"\n      role = \"user\"\n      content = @(\n        @{\n          type = \"input_text\"\n          text = $text\n        }\n      )\n    }\n  )\n  parallel_tool_calls = $true\n  reasoning = @{\n    effort = \"high\"\n    summary = \"auto\"\n  }\n  stream = $true\n  store = $false\n  include = @(\n    \"reasoning.encrypted_content\"\n  )\n}\n\n$body = $bodyObject | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 100 -Compress\n\n$outBase = \"generated\"\n$utf8NoBom = New-Object System.Text.UTF8Encoding($false)\n$tempBodyFile = Join-Path $env:TEMP (\"response-body-\" + [guid]::NewGuid().ToString(\"N\") + \".json\")\n[System.IO.File]::WriteAllText($tempBodyFile, $body, $utf8NoBom)\n\ntry {\n  curl.exe --silent --show-error --no-buffer `\n    -X POST $apiUrl `\n    -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" `\n    -H \"Authorization: Bearer $apiKey\" `\n    --data-binary (\"@\" + $tempBodyFile) |\n  ForEach-Object -Begin {\n    $eventType = $null\n    $dataLines = [System.Collections.Generic.List[string]]::new()\n\n    function Save-Bytes {\n      param([string]$Path, [string]$Base64)\n      [System.IO.File]::WriteAllBytes($Path, [Convert]::FromBase64String($Base64))\n      Write-Host \"Saved $Path\"\n    }\n\n    function Save-ImageGenerationCallResult {\n      param([object]$ImageCall)\n\n      if (-not $ImageCall) { return }\n      if ($ImageCall.type -ne \"image_generation_call\") { return }\n      if (-not $ImageCall.result) { return }\n\n      $ext = if ($ImageCall.output_format) { [string]$ImageCall.output_format } else { \"png\" }\n      $path = Join-Path (Get-Location) \"$outBase.$ext\"\n      Save-Bytes -Path $path -Base64 ([string]$ImageCall.result)\n    }\n\n    function ConvertFrom-JsonCompat {\n      param([string]$Json)\n\n      if ($PSVersionTable.PSVersion.Major -ge 6) {\n        return $Json | ConvertFrom-Json -Depth 100\n      }\n\n      return $Json | ConvertFrom-Json\n    }\n\n    function Flush-SseEvent {\n      param([string]$Type, [System.Collections.Generic.List[string]]$DataLines)\n\n      if (-not $Type -or $DataLines.Count -eq 0) { return }\n\n      $json = ($DataLines -join \"`n\").Trim()\n      if (-not $json -or $json -eq \"[DONE]\") { return }\n\n      try {\n        $obj = ConvertFrom-JsonCompat -Json $json\n      } catch {\n        return\n      }\n\n      switch ($Type) {\n        \"response.output_item.done\" {\n          Save-ImageGenerationCallResult -ImageCall $obj.item\n        }\n\n        \"response.completed\" {\n          $imageCall = @(\n            $obj.response.output |\n            Where-Object { $_.type -eq \"image_generation_call\" -and $_.result }\n          ) | Select-Object -First 1\n\n          Save-ImageGenerationCallResult -ImageCall $imageCall\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  } -Process {\n    $line = [string]$_\n","name":"curl https://r.jina.ai/http...seek.com/post-692204-1"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776871065544}}
{"type":"message","id":"c64355e9","parentId":"60e0a4f7","timestamp":"2026-04-22T15:17:50.391Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_77IDxIWdZWO3C2vUtMeD33mc|fc_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8e69bf24481938dd84a15b3dc5017","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -L --silent 'https://r.jina.ai/http://https://www.nodeseek.com/post-692204-1' | grep -n -i -E 'sub2api|image|images|gpt-image|skill|skills|openai|tool|plugin|脚本|powershell|curl' | sed -n '1,120p'","workdir":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace","yieldMs":2000,"timeout":30},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"curl -L --silent 'https://r.jina.ai/http://https://www.nodeseek.com/post-692204-1' | grep -n -i -E 'sub2api|image|images|gpt-image|skill|skills|openai|tool|plugin|脚本|powershell|curl' | sed -n '1,120p'\",\"workdir\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace\",\"yieldMs\":2000,\"timeout\":30}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":37788,"output":123,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37911,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776871065590,"responseId":"resp_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8e69a52808193975815e3a0bc12cc"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ae9a4d01","parentId":"c64355e9","timestamp":"2026-04-22T15:17:52.185Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_77IDxIWdZWO3C2vUtMeD33mc|fc_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8e69bf24481938dd84a15b3dc5017","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"8:**[![Image 1: logo](https://www.nodeseek.com/static/image/favicon/android-chrome-192x192.png)NodeSeek beta](https://www.nodeseek.com/)**\n37:[![Image 2: hkfires](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/23484.png)](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/23484 \"hkfires\")\n45:昨天，在群里小伙伴的提醒下，我了解到通过反代 Codex 也可以进行图片的生成和编辑了。随即我进行了一番实验，使用 `GPT-Image-1.5` 成功生成了如下图片：\n47:![Image 3](https://img.072899.xyz/2026/04/3cb8c69fac588f10966c91f8e7b50a7b.png)\n49:#### 技术原理：工具调用（Tool Calling）\n61:在 `CLIProxyAPI` 的配置文件中添加以下内容。这里我们将 `gpt-5.4-mini` 映射为不同分辨率的生图模型，并通过 Payload 强制开启 `image_generation` 工具。\n67:      alias: gpt-image-1024x1024\n70:      alias: gpt-image-1024x1536\n73:      alias: gpt-image-1536x1024\n79:        - name: gpt-image-1024x1024\n82:        tools: '[{\"type\":\"image_generation\", \"size\": \"1024x1024\", \"quality\": \"high\", \"background\": \"auto\"}]'\n83:        tool_choice: '{\"type\": \"image_generation\"}'\n85:        - name: gpt-image-1024x1536\n88:        tools: '[{\"type\":\"image_generation\", \"size\": \"1024x1536\", \"quality\": \"high\", \"background\": \"auto\"}]'\n89:        tool_choice: '{\"type\": \"image_generation\"}'\n91:        - name: gpt-image-1536x1024\n94:        tools: '[{\"type\":\"image_generation\", \"size\": \"1536x1024\", \"quality\": \"high\", \"background\": \"auto\"}]'\n95:        tool_choice: '{\"type\": \"image_generation\"}'\n98:添加完成后，我们就可以直接调用 `gpt-image-1024x1024`、`gpt-image-1024x1536` 和 `gpt-image-1536x1024` 这三个自定义模型了。\n102:#### 2. 快速调用脚本 (PowerShell)\n104:由于目前我还未找到好用的生图客户端，我编写了一个简单的 Windows PowerShell 脚本供大家参考。\n108:1.   修改脚本前四行的 `apiUrl`、`apiKey` 等参数。\n109:2.   将完整脚本粘贴至 PowerShell 窗口运行。\n112:```powershell\n115:$model = \"gpt-image-1536x1024\"\n133:  parallel_tool_calls = $true\n153:  curl.exe --silent --show-error --no-buffer `\n168:    function Save-ImageGenerationCallResult {\n169:      param([object]$ImageCall)\n171:      if (-not $ImageCall) { return }\n172:      if ($ImageCall.type -ne \"image_generation_call\") { return }\n173:      if (-not $ImageCall.result) { return }\n175:      $ext = if ($ImageCall.output_format) { [string]$ImageCall.output_format } else { \"png\" }\n177:      Save-Bytes -Path $path -Base64 ([string]$ImageCall.result)\n206:          Save-ImageGenerationCallResult -ImageCall $obj.item\n210:          $imageCall = @(\n212:            Where-Object { $_.type -eq \"image_generation_call\" -and $_.result }\n215:          Save-ImageGenerationCallResult -ImageCall $imageCall\n256:如需了解更详细的参数调整可以参考 [OpenAI 官方文档](https://www.nodeseek.com/jump?to=https%3A%2F%2Fdevelopers.openai.com%2Fapi%2Fdocs%2Fguides%2Fimage-generation)\n260:*   [![Image 4: 大闸泄](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/29905.png)](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/29905 \"大闸泄\") [大闸泄](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/29905) 4days ago  [#1](https://www.nodeseek.com/post-692204-1#1)  \n264:*   [![Image 5: 捷土唛fou](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/40348.png)](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/40348 \"捷土唛fou\") [捷土唛fou](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/40348) 4days ago  [#2](https://www.nodeseek.com/post-692204-1#2)  \n268:*   [![Image 6: 原神糕手](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/42634.png)](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/42634 \"原神糕手\") [原神糕手](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/42634) 4days ago  [#3](https://www.nodeseek.com/post-692204-1#3)  \n269:感谢分享 ![Image 7: xhj003](https://www.nodeseek.com/static/image/sticker/xhj/003.png)\n272:*   [![Image 8: DEBUGBin](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/6678.png)](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/6678 \"DEBUGBin\") [DEBUGBin](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/6678) 4days ago  [#4](https://www.nodeseek.com/post-692204-1#4)  \n276:*   [![Image 9: qiying](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/24891.png)](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/24891 \"qiying\") [qiying](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/24891) 4days ago  [#5](https://www.nodeseek.com/post-692204-1#5)  \n280:*   [![Image 10: ygzst26](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/42901.png)](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/42901 \"ygzst26\") [ygzst26](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/42901) 4days ago  [#6](https://www.nodeseek.com/post-692204-1#6)  \n284:*   [![Image 11: qiying](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/24891.png)](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/24891 \"qiying\") [qiying](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/24891) 4days ago  [#7](https://www.nodeseek.com/post-692204-1#7)  \n285:image_generation是codex内置的工具吗？\n288:*   [![Image 12: hkfires](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/23484.png)](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/23484 \"hkfires\") [hkfires](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/23484)楼主 管理 4days ago  [#8](https://www.nodeseek.com/post-692204-1#8)  \n294:*   [![Image 13: qiying](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/24891.png)](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/24891 \"qiying\") [qiying](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/24891) 4days ago  [#9](https://www.nodeseek.com/post-692204-1#9)  \n298:*   [![Image 14: abcd666](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/13071.png)](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/13071 \"abcd666\") [abcd666](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/13071) 4days ago  [#10](https://www.nodeseek.com/post-692204-1#10)  \n344:[![Image 15: cxlde2](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/54687.png) cxlde2](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/54687)[![Image 16: viphui](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/54686.png) viphui](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/54686)[![Image 17: HelloM](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/54685.png) HelloM](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/54685)[![Image 18: stpk951753](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/54684.png) stpk951753](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/54684)[![Image 19: 168](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/54683.png) 168](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/54683)[![Image 20: minger](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/54682.png) minger](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/54682)[![Image 21: katrina9527](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/54681.png) katrina9527](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/54681)[![Image 22: zacharyzhang](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/54680.png) zacharyzhang](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/54680)\n364:*   [![Image 23](https://www.nodeseek.com/static/image/telegram-app.svg)](https://t.me/nodeseek)\n365:[* ![Image 24](https://www.nodeseek.com/static/image/email-colored.svg)](https://www.nodeseek.com/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#c18dadaeb8a581afaea5a4b2a4a4aaefa2aeac)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1706,"aggregated":"8:**[![Image 1: logo](https://www.nodeseek.com/static/image/favicon/android-chrome-192x192.png)NodeSeek beta](https://www.nodeseek.com/)**\n37:[![Image 2: hkfires](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/23484.png)](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/23484 \"hkfires\")\n45:昨天，在群里小伙伴的提醒下，我了解到通过反代 Codex 也可以进行图片的生成和编辑了。随即我进行了一番实验，使用 `GPT-Image-1.5` 成功生成了如下图片：\n47:![Image 3](https://img.072899.xyz/2026/04/3cb8c69fac588f10966c91f8e7b50a7b.png)\n49:#### 技术原理：工具调用（Tool Calling）\n61:在 `CLIProxyAPI` 的配置文件中添加以下内容。这里我们将 `gpt-5.4-mini` 映射为不同分辨率的生图模型，并通过 Payload 强制开启 `image_generation` 工具。\n67:      alias: gpt-image-1024x1024\n70:      alias: gpt-image-1024x1536\n73:      alias: gpt-image-1536x1024\n79:        - name: gpt-image-1024x1024\n82:        tools: '[{\"type\":\"image_generation\", \"size\": \"1024x1024\", \"quality\": \"high\", \"background\": \"auto\"}]'\n83:        tool_choice: '{\"type\": \"image_generation\"}'\n85:        - name: gpt-image-1024x1536\n88:        tools: '[{\"type\":\"image_generation\", \"size\": \"1024x1536\", \"quality\": \"high\", \"background\": \"auto\"}]'\n89:        tool_choice: '{\"type\": \"image_generation\"}'\n91:        - name: gpt-image-1536x1024\n94:        tools: '[{\"type\":\"image_generation\", \"size\": \"1536x1024\", \"quality\": \"high\", \"background\": \"auto\"}]'\n95:        tool_choice: '{\"type\": \"image_generation\"}'\n98:添加完成后，我们就可以直接调用 `gpt-image-1024x1024`、`gpt-image-1024x1536` 和 `gpt-image-1536x1024` 这三个自定义模型了。\n102:#### 2. 快速调用脚本 (PowerShell)\n104:由于目前我还未找到好用的生图客户端，我编写了一个简单的 Windows PowerShell 脚本供大家参考。\n108:1.   修改脚本前四行的 `apiUrl`、`apiKey` 等参数。\n109:2.   将完整脚本粘贴至 PowerShell 窗口运行。\n112:```powershell\n115:$model = \"gpt-image-1536x1024\"\n133:  parallel_tool_calls = $true\n153:  curl.exe --silent --show-error --no-buffer `\n168:    function Save-ImageGenerationCallResult {\n169:      param([object]$ImageCall)\n171:      if (-not $ImageCall) { return }\n172:      if ($ImageCall.type -ne \"image_generation_call\") { return }\n173:      if (-not $ImageCall.result) { return }\n175:      $ext = if ($ImageCall.output_format) { [string]$ImageCall.output_format } else { \"png\" }\n177:      Save-Bytes -Path $path -Base64 ([string]$ImageCall.result)\n206:          Save-ImageGenerationCallResult -ImageCall $obj.item\n210:          $imageCall = @(\n212:            Where-Object { $_.type -eq \"image_generation_call\" -and $_.result }\n215:          Save-ImageGenerationCallResult -ImageCall $imageCall\n256:如需了解更详细的参数调整可以参考 [OpenAI 官方文档](https://www.nodeseek.com/jump?to=https%3A%2F%2Fdevelopers.openai.com%2Fapi%2Fdocs%2Fguides%2Fimage-generation)\n260:*   [![Image 4: 大闸泄](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/29905.png)](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/29905 \"大闸泄\") [大闸泄](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/29905) 4days ago  [#1](https://www.nodeseek.com/post-692204-1#1)  \n264:*   [![Image 5: 捷土唛fou](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/40348.png)](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/40348 \"捷土唛fou\") [捷土唛fou](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/40348) 4days ago  [#2](https://www.nodeseek.com/post-692204-1#2)  \n268:*   [![Image 6: 原神糕手](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/42634.png)](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/42634 \"原神糕手\") [原神糕手](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/42634) 4days ago  [#3](https://www.nodeseek.com/post-692204-1#3)  \n269:感谢分享 ![Image 7: xhj003](https://www.nodeseek.com/static/image/sticker/xhj/003.png)\n272:*   [![Image 8: DEBUGBin](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/6678.png)](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/6678 \"DEBUGBin\") [DEBUGBin](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/6678) 4days ago  [#4](https://www.nodeseek.com/post-692204-1#4)  \n276:*   [![Image 9: qiying](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/24891.png)](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/24891 \"qiying\") [qiying](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/24891) 4days ago  [#5](https://www.nodeseek.com/post-692204-1#5)  \n280:*   [![Image 10: ygzst26](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/42901.png)](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/42901 \"ygzst26\") [ygzst26](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/42901) 4days ago  [#6](https://www.nodeseek.com/post-692204-1#6)  \n284:*   [![Image 11: qiying](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/24891.png)](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/24891 \"qiying\") [qiying](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/24891) 4days ago  [#7](https://www.nodeseek.com/post-692204-1#7)  \n285:image_generation是codex内置的工具吗？\n288:*   [![Image 12: hkfires](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/23484.png)](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/23484 \"hkfires\") [hkfires](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/23484)楼主 管理 4days ago  [#8](https://www.nodeseek.com/post-692204-1#8)  \n294:*   [![Image 13: qiying](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/24891.png)](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/24891 \"qiying\") [qiying](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/24891) 4days ago  [#9](https://www.nodeseek.com/post-692204-1#9)  \n298:*   [![Image 14: abcd666](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/13071.png)](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/13071 \"abcd666\") [abcd666](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/13071) 4days ago  [#10](https://www.nodeseek.com/post-692204-1#10)  \n344:[![Image 15: cxlde2](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/54687.png) cxlde2](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/54687)[![Image 16: viphui](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/54686.png) viphui](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/54686)[![Image 17: HelloM](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/54685.png) HelloM](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/54685)[![Image 18: stpk951753](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/54684.png) stpk951753](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/54684)[![Image 19: 168](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/54683.png) 168](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/54683)[![Image 20: minger](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/54682.png) minger](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/54682)[![Image 21: katrina9527](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/54681.png) katrina9527](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/54681)[![Image 22: zacharyzhang](https://www.nodeseek.com/avatar/54680.png) zacharyzhang](https://www.nodeseek.com/space/54680)\n364:*   [![Image 23](https://www.nodeseek.com/static/image/telegram-app.svg)](https://t.me/nodeseek)\n365:[* ![Image 24](https://www.nodeseek.com/static/image/email-colored.svg)](https://www.nodeseek.com/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#c18dadaeb8a581afaea5a4b2a4a4aaefa2aeac)","cwd":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776871072147}}
{"type":"message","id":"d6aaf52a","parentId":"ae9a4d01","timestamp":"2026-04-22T15:18:02.766Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_VmVzS5MLCEJQBjMokmALtkUe|fc_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8e6a403788193b65364e039009bde","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -L --silent 'https://r.jina.ai/http://https://www.nodeseek.com/post-692204-1' | sed -n '49,120p'","workdir":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace","yieldMs":2000,"timeout":30},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"curl -L --silent 'https://r.jina.ai/http://https://www.nodeseek.com/post-692204-1' | sed -n '49,120p'\",\"workdir\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace\",\"yieldMs\":2000,\"timeout\":30}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":40255,"output":83,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40338,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776871072188,"responseId":"resp_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8e6a13964819384422a2be589b27d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"168f84bb","parentId":"d6aaf52a","timestamp":"2026-04-22T15:18:04.675Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_VmVzS5MLCEJQBjMokmALtkUe|fc_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8e6a403788193b65364e039009bde","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#### 技术原理：工具调用（Tool Calling）\n\n与 Gemini 使用专用图片模型（如 NanoBanana 系列）的逻辑不同，在 Codex 中，生图功能是通过 **调用工具** 实现的，并不依赖特定的模型名称。\n\n基于这一特性，我们可以利用 `CLIProxyAPI` 的 **模型别名** 配合 **Payload 重写** 功能，自定义一套专属的“文生图模型”。下面我分享一下自己的配置思路和使用方法，希望能起到抛砖引玉的作用。\n\nPS：下文前提是已经安装配置好 `CLIProxyAPI` 并添加了 Codex 的 OAuth 凭证。\n\n* * *\n\n#### 1. 配置文件修改\n\n在 `CLIProxyAPI` 的配置文件中添加以下内容。这里我们将 `gpt-5.4-mini` 映射为不同分辨率的生图模型，并通过 Payload 强制开启 `image_generation` 工具。\n\n```yaml\noauth-model-alias:\n  codex:\n    - name: gpt-5.4-mini\n      alias: gpt-image-1024x1024\n      fork: true\n    - name: gpt-5.4-mini\n      alias: gpt-image-1024x1536\n      fork: true\n    - name: gpt-5.4-mini\n      alias: gpt-image-1536x1024\n      fork: true\n\npayload:\n  override-raw:\n    - models:\n        - name: gpt-image-1024x1024\n          protocol: codex\n      params:\n        tools: '[{\"type\":\"image_generation\", \"size\": \"1024x1024\", \"quality\": \"high\", \"background\": \"auto\"}]'\n        tool_choice: '{\"type\": \"image_generation\"}'\n    - models:\n        - name: gpt-image-1024x1536\n          protocol: codex\n      params:\n        tools: '[{\"type\":\"image_generation\", \"size\": \"1024x1536\", \"quality\": \"high\", \"background\": \"auto\"}]'\n        tool_choice: '{\"type\": \"image_generation\"}'\n    - models:\n        - name: gpt-image-1536x1024\n          protocol: codex\n      params:\n        tools: '[{\"type\":\"image_generation\", \"size\": \"1536x1024\", \"quality\": \"high\", \"background\": \"auto\"}]'\n        tool_choice: '{\"type\": \"image_generation\"}'\n```\n\n添加完成后，我们就可以直接调用 `gpt-image-1024x1024`、`gpt-image-1024x1536` 和 `gpt-image-1536x1024` 这三个自定义模型了。\n\n* * *\n\n#### 2. 快速调用脚本 (PowerShell)\n\n由于目前我还未找到好用的生图客户端，我编写了一个简单的 Windows PowerShell 脚本供大家参考。\n\n**使用方法：**\n\n1.   修改脚本前四行的 `apiUrl`、`apiKey` 等参数。\n2.   将完整脚本粘贴至 PowerShell 窗口运行。\n3.   等待约数十秒，即可在当前运行路径下看到生成的图片。\n\n```powershell\n$apiUrl = \"https://你的CLIProxyAPI地址/v1/responses\"\n$apiKey = \"你的CLIProxyAPI的apikey\"\n$model = \"gpt-image-1536x1024\"\n$text = \"画一张赛博朋克的香港，要有汉字\"\n\n$bodyObject = @{\n  model = $model\n  instructions = \"You are a helpful assistant.\""}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1809,"aggregated":"#### 技术原理：工具调用（Tool Calling）\n\n与 Gemini 使用专用图片模型（如 NanoBanana 系列）的逻辑不同，在 Codex 中，生图功能是通过 **调用工具** 实现的，并不依赖特定的模型名称。\n\n基于这一特性，我们可以利用 `CLIProxyAPI` 的 **模型别名** 配合 **Payload 重写** 功能，自定义一套专属的“文生图模型”。下面我分享一下自己的配置思路和使用方法，希望能起到抛砖引玉的作用。\n\nPS：下文前提是已经安装配置好 `CLIProxyAPI` 并添加了 Codex 的 OAuth 凭证。\n\n* * *\n\n#### 1. 配置文件修改\n\n在 `CLIProxyAPI` 的配置文件中添加以下内容。这里我们将 `gpt-5.4-mini` 映射为不同分辨率的生图模型，并通过 Payload 强制开启 `image_generation` 工具。\n\n```yaml\noauth-model-alias:\n  codex:\n    - name: gpt-5.4-mini\n      alias: gpt-image-1024x1024\n      fork: true\n    - name: gpt-5.4-mini\n      alias: gpt-image-1024x1536\n      fork: true\n    - name: gpt-5.4-mini\n      alias: gpt-image-1536x1024\n      fork: true\n\npayload:\n  override-raw:\n    - models:\n        - name: gpt-image-1024x1024\n          protocol: codex\n      params:\n        tools: '[{\"type\":\"image_generation\", \"size\": \"1024x1024\", \"quality\": \"high\", \"background\": \"auto\"}]'\n        tool_choice: '{\"type\": \"image_generation\"}'\n    - models:\n        - name: gpt-image-1024x1536\n          protocol: codex\n      params:\n        tools: '[{\"type\":\"image_generation\", \"size\": \"1024x1536\", \"quality\": \"high\", \"background\": \"auto\"}]'\n        tool_choice: '{\"type\": \"image_generation\"}'\n    - models:\n        - name: gpt-image-1536x1024\n          protocol: codex\n      params:\n        tools: '[{\"type\":\"image_generation\", \"size\": \"1536x1024\", \"quality\": \"high\", \"background\": \"auto\"}]'\n        tool_choice: '{\"type\": \"image_generation\"}'\n```\n\n添加完成后，我们就可以直接调用 `gpt-image-1024x1024`、`gpt-image-1024x1536` 和 `gpt-image-1536x1024` 这三个自定义模型了。\n\n* * *\n\n#### 2. 快速调用脚本 (PowerShell)\n\n由于目前我还未找到好用的生图客户端，我编写了一个简单的 Windows PowerShell 脚本供大家参考。\n\n**使用方法：**\n\n1.   修改脚本前四行的 `apiUrl`、`apiKey` 等参数。\n2.   将完整脚本粘贴至 PowerShell 窗口运行。\n3.   等待约数十秒，即可在当前运行路径下看到生成的图片。\n\n```powershell\n$apiUrl = \"https://你的CLIProxyAPI地址/v1/responses\"\n$apiKey = \"你的CLIProxyAPI的apikey\"\n$model = \"gpt-image-1536x1024\"\n$text = \"画一张赛博朋克的香港，要有汉字\"\n\n$bodyObject = @{\n  model = $model\n  instructions = \"You are a helpful assistant.\"","cwd":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776871084626}}
{"type":"message","id":"13cce841","parentId":"168f84bb","timestamp":"2026-04-22T15:18:09.759Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a7Rhnq8BmmtsLfO4VrWRbVRQ|fc_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8e6b035648193a3ac9cf0ced8cc0a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace -maxdepth 2 -type f | sed -n '1,200p'","workdir":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace","yieldMs":1000,"timeout":20},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"find /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace -maxdepth 2 -type f | sed -n '1,200p'\",\"workdir\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace\",\"yieldMs\":1000,\"timeout\":20}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":41134,"output":77,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41211,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776871084678,"responseId":"resp_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8e6adb8bc819386c8dcb567476863"}}
