{"type":"message","id":"1a70fc43","parentId":"9bd41a80","timestamp":"2026-04-22T15:20:47.911Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好，那就更顺了。  \n**JSON 配置完全可以做。**\n\n基于你那篇文章的思路，你的 `CLIProxyAPI` 如果是 **JSON 配置**，核心就是把文章里的 YAML 改成 JSON 版，重点仍然是这两块：\n\n1. **模型别名**\n2. **payload 重写，强制启用 `image_generation`**\n\n### 你这边对应的 JSON 思路会是这样\n\n```json\n{\n  \"oauth-model-alias\": {\n    \"codex\": [\n      {\n        \"name\": \"gpt-5.4-mini\",\n        \"alias\": \"gpt-image-1024x1024\",\n        \"fork\": true\n      },\n      {\n        \"name\": \"gpt-5.4-mini\",\n        \"alias\": \"gpt-image-1024x1536\",\n        \"fork\": true\n      },\n      {\n        \"name\": \"gpt-5.4-mini\",\n        \"alias\": \"gpt-image-1536x1024\",\n        \"fork\": true\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"override-raw\": [\n      {\n        \"models\": [\n          {\n            \"name\": \"gpt-image-1024x1024\",\n            \"protocol\": \"codex\"\n          }\n        ],\n        \"params\": {\n          \"tools\": \"[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"image_generation\\\",\\\"size\\\":\\\"1024x1024\\\",\\\"quality\\\":\\\"high\\\",\\\"background\\\":\\\"auto\\\"}]\",\n          \"tool_choice\": \"{\\\"type\\\":\\\"image_generation\\\"}\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"models\": [\n          {\n            \"name\": \"gpt-image-1024x1536\",\n            \"protocol\": \"codex\"\n          }\n        ],\n        \"params\": {\n          \"tools\": \"[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"image_generation\\\",\\\"size\\\":\\\"1024x1536\\\",\\\"quality\\\":\\\"high\\\",\\\"background\\\":\\\"auto\\\"}]\",\n          \"tool_choice\": \"{\\\"type\\\":\\\"image_generation\\\"}\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"models\": [\n          {\n            \"name\": \"gpt-image-1536x1024\",\n            \"protocol\": \"codex\"\n          }\n        ],\n        \"params\": {\n          \"tools\": \"[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"image_generation\\\",\\\"size\\\":\\\"1536x1024\\\",\\\"quality\\\":\\\"high\\\",\\\"background\\\":\\\"auto\\\"}]\",\n          \"tool_choice\": \"{\\\"type\\\":\\\"image_generation\\\"}\"\n        }\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 这意味着什么\n如果你的 `CLIProxyAPI` 确实接受这种 JSON 结构，那我可以继续帮你做成一个真正可用的 skill，专门支持：\n\n- 输入提示词\n- 调你的 `CLIProxyAPI`\n- 走 `/v1/responses`\n- 自动提取 `image_generation_call.result`\n- 保存成 PNG\n\n### 我建议下一步直接做\n我可以直接给你产出一套 **可安装版 skill**，按这个目录：\n\n```text\n~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image/\n├── SKILL.md\n├── EXTEND.example.md\n└── scripts/\n    └── generate-image.sh\n```\n\n### 现在我还差最后 2 个信息\n你发我这两个，我就能把 skill 做到能直接改配置使用：\n\n1. **你的 CLIProxyAPI base URL 长什么样**\n   - 例如：`https://abc.com`\n   - 或 `https://abc.com/v1`\n\n2. **你想在什么环境跑脚本**\n   - Linux\n   - macOS\n   - Windows PowerShell\n\n你只要回我一句像这样就行：\n\n`baseUrl 是 https://xxx ，Linux`\n\n我就继续给你生成完整 skill。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8e74164888193bcfeb7b9fa56ab92\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":11610,"output":789,"cacheRead":34560,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46959,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776871229293,"responseId":"resp_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8e73e9d2481939b71dec9cc4c42f9"}}
