{"type":"message","id":"5aa483f5","parentId":"a20c4cba","timestamp":"2026-04-22T15:22:29.670Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2xcaS6vNDGjTXVNns5ZVfYCi|fc_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8e7ab084c81939736611a4bc91cba","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/sub2api-gpt-image-install/README.md","content":"# sub2api-gpt-image\n\n给 OpenClaw 用的一个轻量 skill 模板，适用于通过 CLIProxyAPI / sub2api 这类 OpenAI 兼容网关调用 `POST /v1/responses`，并强制启用 `image_generation` 工具来生图。\n\n## 你的环境\n\n- Base URL: `http://china.unicom-online.cloud:8317/v1`\n- 平台: Linux\n\n## 目录结构\n\n```text\nsub2api-gpt-image-install/\n├── README.md\n├── SKILL.md\n├── EXTEND.example.md\n└── scripts/\n    └── generate-image.sh\n```\n\n## 安装方法\n\n把整个目录复制到：\n\n```bash\nmkdir -p ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image\ncp -r /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/sub2api-gpt-image-install/* ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image/\nchmod +x ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image/scripts/generate-image.sh\n```\n\n## 你需要做的配置\n\n复制一份示例配置：\n\n```bash\nmkdir -p ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image\ncp ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image/EXTEND.example.md ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image/EXTEND.md\n```\n\n然后填写：\n- `base_url`\n- `api_key`\n- 默认模型别名\n- 默认输出目录\n\n## 直接调用示例\n\n```bash\nbash ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image/scripts/generate-image.sh \\\n  --base-url 'http://china.unicom-online.cloud:8317/v1' \\\n  --api-key '你的CLIProxyAPI密钥' \\\n  --model 'gpt-image-1024x1024' \\\n  --prompt '画一张赛博朋克香港夜景，要有中文招牌，电影感' \\\n  --output '/tmp/cyberpunk-hk.png'\n```\n\n## 说明\n\n这个脚本依赖：\n- `curl`\n- `jq`\n- `base64`\n\n如果响应里包含 `image_generation_call.result`，脚本会自动解码并保存成图片。\n"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/sub2api-gpt-image-install/README.md\",\"content\":\"# sub2api-gpt-image\\n\\n给 OpenClaw 用的一个轻量 skill 模板，适用于通过 CLIProxyAPI / sub2api 这类 OpenAI 兼容网关调用 `POST /v1/responses`，并强制启用 `image_generation` 工具来生图。\\n\\n## 你的环境\\n\\n- Base URL: `http://china.unicom-online.cloud:8317/v1`\\n- 平台: Linux\\n\\n## 目录结构\\n\\n```text\\nsub2api-gpt-image-install/\\n├── README.md\\n├── SKILL.md\\n├── EXTEND.example.md\\n└── scripts/\\n    └── generate-image.sh\\n```\\n\\n## 安装方法\\n\\n把整个目录复制到：\\n\\n```bash\\nmkdir -p ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image\\ncp -r /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/sub2api-gpt-image-install/* ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image/\\nchmod +x ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image/scripts/generate-image.sh\\n```\\n\\n## 你需要做的配置\\n\\n复制一份示例配置：\\n\\n```bash\\nmkdir -p ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image\\ncp ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image/EXTEND.example.md ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image/EXTEND.md\\n```\\n\\n然后填写：\\n- `base_url`\\n- `api_key`\\n- 默认模型别名\\n- 默认输出目录\\n\\n## 直接调用示例\\n\\n```bash\\nbash ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image/scripts/generate-image.sh \\\\\\n  --base-url 'http://china.unicom-online.cloud:8317/v1' \\\\\\n  --api-key '你的CLIProxyAPI密钥' \\\\\\n  --model 'gpt-image-1024x1024' \\\\\\n  --prompt '画一张赛博朋克香港夜景，要有中文招牌，电影感' \\\\\\n  --output '/tmp/cyberpunk-hk.png'\\n```\\n\\n## 说明\\n\\n这个脚本依赖：\\n- `curl`\\n- `jq`\\n- `base64`\\n\\n如果响应里包含 `image_generation_call.result`，脚本会自动解码并保存成图片。\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":47198,"output":583,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47781,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776871335057,"responseId":"resp_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8e7a867788193b46b28ca430df64b"}}
