{"type":"message","id":"975871c1","parentId":"7ff1203e","timestamp":"2026-04-22T15:23:27.152Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好了，我已经按你的环境做成了一个 **Linux 可安装版 skill 模板**。\n\n位置在：\n\n`/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/sub2api-gpt-image-install`\n\n里面有：\n\n- `README.md`\n- `SKILL.md`\n- `EXTEND.example.md`\n- `scripts/generate-image.sh`\n\n### 你的参数我已经写进去了\n- Base URL: `http://china.unicom-online.cloud:8317/v1`\n- 平台：Linux\n\n### 它是干什么的\n这个 skill 模板适合你这种场景：\n\n- `CLIProxyAPI` 是 **JSON 配置**\n- 走 **`/v1/responses`**\n- 通过 **模型别名 + payload rewrite**\n- 强制启用 `image_generation`\n- 自动把返回的 base64 图片保存为 PNG\n\n### 你现在可以这样安装\n```bash\nmkdir -p ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image\ncp -r /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/sub2api-gpt-image-install/* ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image/\nchmod +x ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image/scripts/generate-image.sh\ncp ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image/EXTEND.example.md ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image/EXTEND.md\n```\n\n### 然后这样调用\n```bash\nbash ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image/scripts/generate-image.sh \\\n  --base-url 'http://china.unicom-online.cloud:8317/v1' \\\n  --api-key '你的CLIProxyAPI密钥' \\\n  --model 'gpt-image-1024x1024' \\\n  --prompt '画一张赛博朋克香港夜景，要有中文招牌，电影感' \\\n  --output '/tmp/cyberpunk-hk.png'\n```\n\n### 下一步我建议\n如果你愿意，我可以继续帮你做两件事里的任意一个：\n\n1. **把你的 JSON 配置文件也一起写好**\n2. **直接帮你做一次联调排错**\n\n如果要继续，直接把你的 `CLIProxyAPI` 当前 JSON 配置贴给我。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8e7e5f92081938515831ade187669\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":49293,"output":496,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49789,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776871394407,"responseId":"resp_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8e7e3ae4481938e09a6de02a86a2d"}}
