{"type":"message","id":"33fc4755","parentId":"cb2a3aaa","timestamp":"2026-04-22T15:26:16.562Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我替你跑了，结果已经很明确：\n\n### 当前报错\n```json\n{\n  \"error\": {\n    \"message\": \"unknown provider for model gpt-image-1024x1024\",\n    \"type\": \"server_error\",\n    \"code\": \"internal_server_error\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 这说明什么\n不是脚本坏了，也不是提示词问题。  \n而是你的 **CLIProxyAPI / sub2api 服务端还没有认识 `gpt-image-1024x1024` 这个模型别名**。\n\n也就是说，**服务端别名配置还没生效**，或者根本还没加。\n\n---\n\n## 你现在缺的是服务端这一步\n你需要在 `CLIProxyAPI` 的 **JSON 配置** 里加上两类配置：\n\n### 1. 模型别名\n把 `gpt-5.4-mini` 映射成：\n- `gpt-image-1024x1024`\n- `gpt-image-1024x1536`\n- `gpt-image-1536x1024`\n\n### 2. payload 重写\n给这些别名强制注入：\n- `tools: [{\"type\":\"image_generation\", ...}]`\n- `tool_choice: {\"type\":\"image_generation\"}`\n\n---\n\n## 你可以直接参考这个 JSON 片段\n\n```json\n{\n  \"oauth-model-alias\": {\n    \"codex\": [\n      {\n        \"name\": \"gpt-5.4-mini\",\n        \"alias\": \"gpt-image-1024x1024\",\n        \"fork\": true\n      },\n      {\n        \"name\": \"gpt-5.4-mini\",\n        \"alias\": \"gpt-image-1024x1536\",\n        \"fork\": true\n      },\n      {\n        \"name\": \"gpt-5.4-mini\",\n        \"alias\": \"gpt-image-1536x1024\",\n        \"fork\": true\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"override-raw\": [\n      {\n        \"models\": [\n          {\n            \"name\": \"gpt-image-1024x1024\",\n            \"protocol\": \"codex\"\n          }\n        ],\n        \"params\": {\n          \"tools\": \"[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"image_generation\\\",\\\"size\\\":\\\"1024x1024\\\",\\\"quality\\\":\\\"high\\\",\\\"background\\\":\\\"auto\\\"}]\",\n          \"tool_choice\": \"{\\\"type\\\":\\\"image_generation\\\"}\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"models\": [\n          {\n            \"name\": \"gpt-image-1024x1536\",\n            \"protocol\": \"codex\"\n          }\n        ],\n        \"params\": {\n          \"tools\": \"[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"image_generation\\\",\\\"size\\\":\\\"1024x1536\\\",\\\"quality\\\":\\\"high\\\",\\\"background\\\":\\\"auto\\\"}]\",\n          \"tool_choice\": \"{\\\"type\\\":\\\"image_generation\\\"}\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"models\": [\n          {\n            \"name\": \"gpt-image-1536x1024\",\n            \"protocol\": \"codex\"\n          }\n        ],\n        \"params\": {\n          \"tools\": \"[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"image_generation\\\",\\\"size\\\":\\\"1536x1024\\\",\\\"quality\\\":\\\"high\\\",\\\"background\\\":\\\"auto\\\"}]\",\n          \"tool_choice\": \"{\\\"type\\\":\\\"image_generation\\\"}\"\n        }\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 结论\n你这一步已经验证出一个关键事实：\n\n**你的网关地址能通，但模型别名 `gpt-image-1024x1024` 还没在服务端配置好。**\n\n如果你愿意，下一步最省事的方式是：\n\n**把你当前完整的 CLIProxyAPI JSON 配置贴给我**\n\n我直接帮你改成可用版。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8e889f37081938f62d1242bd9e198\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":13708,"output":795,"cacheRead":36480,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50983,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776871558997,"responseId":"resp_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8e887ccf481938a9d3f463535ac95"}}
