{"type":"message","id":"1778d914","parentId":"cd0952c2","timestamp":"2026-04-22T15:29:01.901Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"那就对上了。\n\n你的服务端现在**确实就是 `gpt-draw-*` 这一套别名**，不是 `gpt-image-*`。  \n所以前面的报错其实已经解释通了。\n\n### 结论\n你服务端当前可用的模型名应该是：\n\n- `gpt-draw-1024x1024`\n- `gpt-draw-1024x1536`\n- `gpt-draw-1536x1024`\n\n### 所以你客户端命令必须改成\n```bash\n--model 'gpt-draw-1024x1024'\n```\n\n完整就是：\n\n```bash\nbash ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image/scripts/generate-image.sh \\\n  --base-url 'http://china.unicom-online.cloud:8317/v1' \\\n  --api-key '48ch-wzC2qzxmQIBPq8mMXbQXRi454v8' \\\n  --model 'gpt-draw-1024x1024' \\\n  --prompt '画一张赛博朋克香港夜景，要有中文招牌，电影感' \\\n  --output '/tmp/cyberpunk-hk.png'\n```\n\n### 还有一个我建议你顺手改的地方\n为了避免以后混淆，你可以二选一：\n\n1. **继续保留服务端 `gpt-draw-*`**\n   - 那我把 skill 默认模型也改成 `gpt-draw-1024x1024`\n\n2. **把服务端别名统一改成 `gpt-image-*`**\n   - 跟文章一致，后面更不容易记混\n\n我个人更推荐 **统一成一种命名**，不然之后很容易再次撞上这种错。\n\n如果你要，我下一条可以直接帮你：\n- 把 skill 里的默认模型改成 `gpt-draw-1024x1024`\n- 顺手给你一版整理好的服务端配置文本","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8e935d534819393e97cd073100d7e\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":51917,"output":432,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52349,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776871728167,"responseId":"resp_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8e9318560819384f28a875834bc29"}}
