{"type":"message","id":"35522cf0","parentId":"a2a68ff5","timestamp":"2026-04-22T15:33:44.330Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"有进展了，这次错误已经变了，我挺确定我们更接近了。\n\n### 现在的报错\n```json\n{\n  \"error\": {\n    \"message\": \"Tool choice 'image_generation' not found in 'tools' parameter.\",\n    \"type\": \"invalid_request_error\",\n    \"param\": \"tool_choice\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 这说明什么\n`gpt-image-1024x1024` 这个模型别名**已经被识别到了**，所以之前那个：\n\n- `unknown provider for model ...`\n\n已经过去了，说明 **alias 生效了**。\n\n但现在新的问题是：\n\n**服务端注入进去的 `tools` 没有被正确当成 tools 数组识别。**\n\n最常见原因是这一层配置里，`tools` 和 `tool_choice` 被当成了**字符串**，而不是 JSON 对象 / JSON 数组。\n\n---\n\n## 你现在这段配置的问题点\n你现在大概率写的是这种：\n\n```yaml\ntools: '[{\"type\":\"image_generation\", \"size\": \"1024x1024\", \"quality\": \"high\", \"background\": \"auto\"}]'\ntool_choice: '{\"type\": \"image_generation\"}'\n```\n\n注意外面那层单引号。  \n这会让某些服务端把它当成**纯字符串**，而不是结构化 JSON。\n\n---\n\n## 你应该改成这种\n如果你的 `CLIProxyAPI` 支持对象结构，优先用这个：\n\n```yaml\npayload:\n  override-raw:\n    - models:\n        - name: gpt-image-1024x1024\n          protocol: codex\n      params:\n        tools:\n          - type: image_generation\n            size: 1024x1024\n            quality: high\n            background: auto\n        tool_choice:\n          type: image_generation\n```\n\n另外两个尺寸同理：\n\n```yaml\n    - models:\n        - name: gpt-image-1024x1536\n          protocol: codex\n      params:\n        tools:\n          - type: image_generation\n            size: 1024x1536\n            quality: high\n            background: auto\n        tool_choice:\n          type: image_generation\n\n    - models:\n        - name: gpt-image-1536x1024\n          protocol: codex\n      params:\n        tools:\n          - type: image_generation\n            size: 1536x1024\n            quality: high\n            background: auto\n        tool_choice:\n          type: image_generation\n```\n\n---\n\n## 结论\n当前状态已经变成：\n\n- ✅ base URL 通\n- ✅ alias 生效\n- ❌ `tools` 注入格式不对\n\n也就是说，**现在不是大方向错了，而是只差 payload 格式这一层。**\n\n如果你愿意，我建议你下一步直接把 **CLIProxyAPI 当前完整配置文件** 发我，我帮你改成一版更稳的最终版。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8ea4c5b908193a38809ba82fdf0bb\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":53793,"output":641,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54434,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776872008088,"responseId":"resp_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8ea49e36c8193bafd9c46c779e288"}}
