{"type":"message","id":"265e9071","parentId":"06fbdbed","timestamp":"2026-04-22T15:35:12.523Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这份配置里，**问题还在**，而且我现在基本能明确指出来：\n\n## 核心问题\n你现在的 `tools` 和 `tool_choice` 还是写成了**字符串**：\n\n```yaml\ntools: '[{\"type\":\"image_generation\", ...}]'\ntool_choice: '{\"type\": \"image_generation\"}'\n```\n\n而你当前服务端的行为表明，它**没有把这两个字符串再解析成 JSON**，所以才会报：\n\n> Tool choice 'image_generation' not found in 'tools' parameter.\n\n也就是说，服务端看到的很可能是：\n- `tools = \"一整段字符串\"`\n- `tool_choice = \"一整段字符串\"`\n\n而不是：\n- `tools = 数组`\n- `tool_choice = 对象`\n\n---\n\n# 你应该改成这种结构化写法\n\n## 正确 YAML 版本\n```yaml\noauth-model-alias:\n  codex:\n    - name: gpt-5.4-mini\n      alias: gpt-image-1024x1024\n      fork: true\n    - name: gpt-5.4-mini\n      alias: gpt-image-1024x1536\n      fork: true\n    - name: gpt-5.4-mini\n      alias: gpt-image-1536x1024\n      fork: true\n\npayload:\n  override-raw:\n    - models:\n        - name: gpt-image-1024x1024\n          protocol: codex\n      params:\n        tools:\n          - type: image_generation\n            size: 1024x1024\n            quality: high\n            background: auto\n        tool_choice:\n          type: image_generation\n\n    - models:\n        - name: gpt-image-1024x1536\n          protocol: codex\n      params:\n        tools:\n          - type: image_generation\n            size: 1024x1536\n            quality: high\n            background: auto\n        tool_choice:\n          type: image_generation\n\n    - models:\n        - name: gpt-image-1536x1024\n          protocol: codex\n      params:\n        tools:\n          - type: image_generation\n            size: 1536x1024\n            quality: high\n            background: auto\n        tool_choice:\n          type: image_generation\n```\n\n---\n\n## 为什么这版更对\n因为这次是：\n\n- `tools` = 真正的数组\n- `tool_choice` = 真正的对象\n\n而不是字符串。\n\n---\n\n## 你现在的状态其实已经很好判断了\n目前排查结果是：\n\n- ✅ `gpt-image-*` alias 已经生效\n- ✅ 请求已经打到服务端\n- ❌ payload 重写里的 `tools/tool_choice` 格式错了\n\n所以现在**只剩这一个点**。\n\n---\n\n## 我建议你下一步就做这个\n1. 把服务端配置改成我上面这版\n2. 重启 / reload `CLIProxyAPI`\n3. 再跑你这条命令\n\n```bash\nbash ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image/scripts/generate-image.sh \\\n --base-url 'http://china.unicom-online.cloud:8317/v1' \\\n --api-key '48ch-wzC2qzxmQIBPq8mMXbQXRi454v8' \\\n --model 'gpt-image-1024x1024' \\\n --prompt '画一张赛博朋克香港夜景，要有中文招牌，电影感' \\\n --output '/tmp/cyberpunk-hk.png'\n```\n\n如果你愿意，我下一条可以直接给你一份**可复制的完整最终配置块**，你不用自己再整理。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8eaa1aa9c8193bf5a8317a88201fa\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":54791,"output":806,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55597,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776872089067,"responseId":"resp_08875cf3083ad23c0169e8ea9d66f0819394ffb284b965eeba"}}
