{"type":"message","id":"597c87dd","parentId":"e93bc0c6","timestamp":"2026-04-22T15:36:08.562Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好，我直接给你一份 **可复制的最终版配置块**。  \n你把对应部分替换进 `CLIProxyAPI` 配置文件里就行。\n\n## 最终推荐配置\n\n```yaml\nusage-statistics-enabled: true\n\noauth-model-alias:\n  codex:\n    - name: gpt-5.4-mini\n      alias: gpt-image-1024x1024\n      fork: true\n    - name: gpt-5.4-mini\n      alias: gpt-image-1024x1536\n      fork: true\n    - name: gpt-5.4-mini\n      alias: gpt-image-1536x1024\n      fork: true\n\npayload:\n  override-raw:\n    - models:\n        - name: gpt-image-1024x1024\n          protocol: codex\n      params:\n        tools:\n          - type: image_generation\n            size: 1024x1024\n            quality: high\n            background: auto\n        tool_choice:\n          type: image_generation\n\n    - models:\n        - name: gpt-image-1024x1536\n          protocol: codex\n      params:\n        tools:\n          - type: image_generation\n            size: 1024x1536\n            quality: high\n            background: auto\n        tool_choice:\n          type: image_generation\n\n    - models:\n        - name: gpt-image-1536x1024\n          protocol: codex\n      params:\n        tools:\n          - type: image_generation\n            size: 1536x1024\n            quality: high\n            background: auto\n        tool_choice:\n          type: image_generation\n```\n\n## 你做完后要做这 2 步\n1. **保存配置**\n2. **重启或 reload CLIProxyAPI**\n\n## 然后再跑这条命令\n```bash\nbash ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image/scripts/generate-image.sh \\\n  --base-url 'http://china.unicom-online.cloud:8317/v1' \\\n  --api-key '48ch-wzC2qzxmQIBPq8mMXbQXRi454v8' \\\n  --model 'gpt-image-1024x1024' \\\n  --prompt '画一张赛博朋克香港夜景，要有中文招牌，电影感' \\\n  --output '/tmp/cyberpunk-hk.png'\n```\n\n## 这次成功的标志\n如果配置正确，下一次应该：\n- 不再报 `unknown provider`\n- 不再报 `tool choice not found`\n- 而是直接输出类似：\n  - `Saved to /tmp/cyberpunk-hk.png`\n\n如果你跑完愿意，把新报错或结果直接贴我，我继续陪你对到通。